{"tid":1066884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大規模拒絕交稅令司法癱瘓會唔會係示威外既出路","createTime":"2019-03-18T07:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T14:49:48.000Z","uid":46906,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6225b11784d0070199ca8447cc84c672466d48ca","tid":1066884,"uid":46906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"既然成日話政府亂咁使納稅人既錢<br />\n咁不如坐言起行拒絕交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然可能響應既人加埋筆錢都唔夠有錢佬交既一個零頭<br />\n但如果要控告晒依班人就要浪費大量人力物力去做<br />\n算唔算係一個除左示威之外既有效表達意見手段？<br />\n<br />\n非暴力<br />\n但對社會有一定沖擊<br />\n但前提係規模起碼有佔中果陣咁廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d61900d76e7eee181aa92dbaca9e47cf4227b8","tid":1066884,"uid":68556,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:37:58.000Z","msg":"欠稅可以扣戶口  扣僱主<br />\n大部分嘅追稅都係電腦做，<br />\n淨低果d， 廢青去唔到的果個銀碼。"},{"pid":"1aec1237ec7476c145a9fcf9ab2d38069fa8fe2b","tid":1066884,"uid":216477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce40d66e2f5894fcc423a35160440ec93e5fdf2e","tid":1066884,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"14年講到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b9239824eb492775d19727a64612da72b4920e","tid":1066884,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"全港僅三分一打工仔繳付　學者倡撤薪俸稅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1058019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1058019</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a299607de1e852c82709243107b9a27334645dd","tid":1066884,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"講拒絕交稅嗰啲基本唔使交稅 ?"},{"pid":"de660c5bdae56a2f4a4d97887018c7de44ad3a35","tid":1066884,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"電腦會自動加你附加費<img s